<item>
            <title>[LU-9411] sanity test_27D: interop 2.9.0&lt;-&gt;master llapi_layout_test 30, 31 failure</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9411</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/a05ca6d8-2548-11e7-9de9-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/a05ca6d8-2548-11e7-9de9-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_27D failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt; test 30: create composite file, traverse components ........ fail (exit status 1)
llapi_layout_test: llapi_layout_test.c:1447: test31: assertion &apos;fd &amp;gt;= 0&apos; failed: path = /mnt/lustre/d27D.sanity/f31, fd = -1, errno = 22
 test 31: add/delete component to/from existing file ........ fail (exit status 1)
 sanity test_27D: @@@@@@ FAIL: llapi_layout_test failed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test should be skipped if MDS does not support PFL.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 27D&lt;/p&gt;</description>
